headline: KLA Hits Highs Amid Massive Big Tech AI Spend; Accelerating Growth, Earnings On Watch
summary: KLA is in a buy zone above a 48-week-long consolidation's buy point of 896.32, according to IBD MarketSurge.  KLA stock is Tuesday's selection for IBD 50 Stocks To Watch.  Shares have rallied as sales and earnings growth accelerated over the past four quarters.
